name: dart-collection
comment: Classes and utilities that supplement the collection support in dart:core.

class.name: LinkedListEntry
class.preview: An object that can be an element in a dart-collection.LinkedList.

class.name: LinkedList
class.preview: A specialized double-linked list of elements that extends dart-collection.LinkedListEntry.

class.name: SplayTreeSet
class.preview: A dart-core.Set of objects that can be ordered relative to each other.

class.name: SplayTreeMap
class.preview: A dart-core.Map of objects that can be ordered relative to each other.

class.name: DoubleLinkedQueue
class.preview: A dart-collection.Queue implementation based on a double-linked list.

class.name: DoubleLinkedQueueEntry
class.preview: An entry in a doubly linked list. It contains a pointer to the next entry, the previous entry, and the boxed element.

class.name: Queue
class.preview: A dart-collection.Queue is a collection that can be manipulated at both ends. One can iterate over the elements of a queue through forEach or with an dart-core.Iterator.

class.name: Maps
class.preview: Helper class which implements complex dart-core.Map operations in term of basic ones (dart-core.Map.keys, Map.operator , Map.operator = and dart-core.Map.remove.) Not all methods are necessary to implement each particular operation.

class.name: HasNextIterator
class.preview: The dart-collection.HasNextIterator class wraps an dart-core.Iterator and provides methods to iterate over an object using hasNext and next.
